data.description: Custom built and recently updated, this lovely Green Hills home is situated on 0.55 acres and is convenient to schools, shopping and restaurants. This home checks all the boxes...primary bedroom on main level, bedrooms w/en suite baths, gorgeous millwork and built-ins, kitchen open to family room, an oversized, four-season back porch, dedicated home office, butler's pantry, zoned for Julia Green Elementary, two car garage, extra storage and a back yard. This home has been immaculately maintained and is a true gem.
